{
  "stem": "214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can assure you there wasn't-- so, but I remember it-- and then the winter came, and then things were getting harder and harder just to live.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not going to anymore to those peasant villages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember there was this one other tenant in our-- I don't know-- it-- it was like a house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were stairs up, we lived downstairs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were maybe three or four families that lived there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this man-- and everybody was looking to find some-- something to do to earn some living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember that this was for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He came to my parents-- and of course, this was-- meant me-- would I go into business with him?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He will-- he will go out into the villages and bring wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I mean the houses were heated by-- by wood or by coal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean there was no central heating, especially in the small places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Most of the houses didn't even have any indoor [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] plumbing and water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and-- and that I should-- and I should become this-- say, I should go to some of those so-called families that are well recognized in Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them was Ben's brother's family, also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I should go and try to, you know, get the orders for this wood, then we will deliver it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was going maybe for about, I don't know, maybe a month.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was not a very good saleslady, I don't think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto-- and then, of course, this was that whole big enterprise that was the brainchild of my cousin, who-- he was from Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had very many, actually very many, Polish, non-Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
